body:
Insert the following documents that define synonym mappings:

**Input:**

```shell
 db.attire_synonyms.insertMany([
   {
     "mappingType": "equivalent",
     "synonyms": ["dress", "apparel", "attire"]
   },
   {
     "mappingType": "explicit",
     "input": ["hat"],
     "synonyms": ["hat", "fedora", "headgear"]
   }
 ])
```

**Output:**

```shell
{
  "acknowledged" : true,
  "insertedIds" : [
    ObjectId("..."),
    ObjectId("...")
  ]
}
```
